{"tid":1605082,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇斯克查：我已打造好防守 冬窗準備提升進攻","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:32:47.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbc1482bdbd66a93ec3be7166473065d2980c07","tid":1605082,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"新賽季曼聯戰績不佳，如今只能排在英超積分榜第11名的位置，蘇斯克查（Ole Solskj&aelig;r）分析了曼聯如今的窘境，他直言將會通過轉會市場解決問題。<br />\n  蘇帥表示：「我們放走了山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）和盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku），所以下一步我們肯定得買入進攻球員，這是顯而易見的。我們現在正在尋找一些增加球隊創造力和入球的球員。」<br />\n<br />\n  「當然，我們也需要進更多的球，正如我之前所說的，我們正在改進我們在進攻層面的模式、配合度。」《鏡報》認為，蘇帥言下之意是，明年一月會買入前鋒加強進攻。<br />\n  「我們會從基礎開始，一步一步做起。當然了，我們現在的防守就做的很不錯，但我對球隊的進攻感覺很不滿意。」"},{"pid":"0a4afa2e8f09565912857110d8d8c459beb4c826","tid":1605082,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"留到1月先諗"},{"pid":"af6da880bb97179bc9c3eaf4b799d5df61cbc0b3","tid":1605082,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[國際文宣]</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日香港, 明日世界</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Hong Kong's today, The world's tomorrow</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">SHARE 去比利事同智利!!!<br />\n等<span style=\"color: red;\">山齊士、盧卡古</span>都知道香港發生乜事!!!</span></strong><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3 分鐘 12 張圖 「今日香港, 明日世界」</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604879</a></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5EkK3S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5EkK3S.png&h=9cc64728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<sp